{"tid":95854,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下關於big 4係final year請人既問題","createTime":"2017-01-26T10:50:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T22:03:58.000Z","uid":79654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"04a5261178e4eda594aa20dc63bfa906916d6443","tid":95854,"uid":79654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T10:50:21.000Z","msg":"唔好意思打攪曬大家 <br />\n不過我想問下大家既睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我而家讀緊Year 3既Accountancy <br />\n因為屋企既原因所以Year 2無去apply exchange 好彩間U好好俾我係Year 3可以再apply一次 如果成功既話Final Year Sem 1就可以起程<br />\n<br />\n但係Final Year既Sem 1咁岩撞正左Big 4請freshgrade既時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我果陣唔會係香港所以唔會去到佢地既recruitment booth<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為我上網都搵唔到我呢個case<br />\n所以我想問下係big 4做緊既朋友可唔可以同我分享一下我應該點做..?有無野要準備架?要拎offer係咪只有果段時間?<br />\n<br />\n太過無知對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3c55861330ad82fc559035cf4c570ed067e7396","tid":95854,"uid":79654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T17:54:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42e0cde82ed9c1be2a9b7b41bf98c3daa2e685d9","tid":95854,"uid":28271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T04:31:14.000Z","msg":"係會好蝕抵<br />\nBig 4大部分local student recruitment時間係9月至11月<br />\n你好彩嘅話，佢應該會group埋你去overseas student果堆12月interview，但到時佢已經請咗好多人"},{"pid":"aa3d856254f473ffb578ded0a2a8f15998b6a826","tid":95854,"uid":79654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T10:19:20.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /